3. ğŸ–¥ï¸ Server & Endpoint Hardening
3.1 Operating Systems
Mixed OS landscape: Windows Server 2016, Ubuntu 20.04
No standard hardening baseline applied: âŒ
Windows SMBv1 still enabled: âŒ
3.2 Endpoint Protection
Antivirus: Windows Defender + CrowdStrike Falcon (partial deployment)
No endpoint detection on legacy MacBooks (HR/Marketing): âŒ
3.3 Patch Management
Linux servers patched monthly via cron script: âœ…
Windows updates delayed for "compatibility": âŒ
3.4 Recommendations
Disable SMBv1 across all Windows hosts.
